Story*
Once upon a time in a forest, there lived a monkey who
resided on a jamun tree which was on the banks of a river.
In the same forest, there lived a croc and his wife.

One day the crocodile, came to the banks of the river and
retsed under the tree.
The kind-hearted monkey offered him sme fruits.The crocodile
came back the next day for more fruits as he loved them.
As days passed by, the croc and the monkey became good friends.

One day the monkey sent some fruits for the crocs wife .
 She ate the fruits and loved them but was jealous as she did
not like her husband spending time with the monkey.
She told her husband , " .."